"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-carlos-yulo-goes-glory-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9998451061016289, \"rank\": 0.0001549167672963926, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kim Kyung-hoon/Reuters  One thing Filipino gymnastics star Carlos Yulo has learned as he sees action in his second Olympics is that it all comes down to him, no one else.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9873399058058929, \"rank\": 0.008244861377988272, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999894962457, \"rank\": 1.05038485319149e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.951227523527957, \"rank\": 0.05115193749027141, \"text\": \"Filipino\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 177, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo heads into the Paris Games in France with the same medal aspirations, but this time, he is more sure of himself three years after going home empty-handed from his maiden Olympic stint in Tokyo, Japan.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999719128242802, \"rank\": 1.8691936996079082e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999976807885, \"rank\": 2.3189862561152066e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9991312592428049, \"rank\": 0.0008666837423597408, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I should focus on myself and let the other gymnasts do what they do,\\\" said Yulo in a mix of Filipino and English when asked about the lessons he picked up from his Tokyo Games run.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all worked hard and we all worked ourselves to exhaustion in training.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I should focus on where I am at and be confident of my moves,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I should not get carried away by my mood and I should trust what I practiced.\\\"\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then 21 years old, Yulo competed in Tokyo as a legitimate medal contender, having won bronze and gold in floor exercise in the 2018 and 2019 editions of the World Artistic Gymnastics Championships, respectively.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999976807885, \"rank\": 2.3189862561152066e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997703526, \"rank\": 2.292766988281687e-10, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Yulo surprisingly finished a distant 44th place in the floor exercise qualification.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He gave himself a medal chance by reaching thevault finals, although he fell a fraction of a point short of a podium spot as he placed fourth.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As painful as it was not being able to meet those lofty expectations, his campaign in Tokyo helped Yulo become braver and smarter in his approach.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999976807885, \"rank\": 2.3189862561152066e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I learned to move confidently and perform what I worked hard for in practice,\\\" said Yulo in an episode ofRappler Talk Sports.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I noticed I was a bit shy back then, so I was not able to truly show what I was capable of doing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, Yulo is expected to vie for gold in the floor exercise and vault - apparatuses where he is a former world champion.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999990682227, \"rank\": 9.319059927802097e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And his impressive showing in the previous Asian Men's Artistic Gymnastics Championship in Tashkent, Uzbekistan, where he emerged as the best performing gymnast withfour golds, augurs well for his Olympic chances.\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999997608029, \"rank\": 2.3941206086237314e-10, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997703526, \"rank\": 2.292766988281687e-10, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tashkent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0401028737337888e-16, \"text\": \"Tashkent\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tashkent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tashkent\"}, {\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999996612241949, \"rank\": 3.279674988835079e-07, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo ruled the floor exercise with 14.933 points and topped the vault with an average of 14.883 points.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If he recorded the same scores in Tokyo, Yulo would have tied floor exercise titlist Artem Dolgopyat of Israel (14.933) and edged vault winner Shin Jea-Hwan of South Korea (14.783).\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999976807885, \"rank\": 2.3189862561152066e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artem_Dolgopyat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Artem Dolgopyat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artem_Dolgopyat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artem_Dolgopyat\"}, {\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9697872449914261, \"rank\": 0.029409888168930393, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it should be noted that Yulo competed in the Asian championships without the pressure of having to go up against some of the best gymnasts in the continent, with powerhouse Japan missing action in the senior division.\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2411, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999997608029, \"rank\": 2.3941206086237314e-10, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.