.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee_athletes_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.364534999398098e-22, \"text\": \"Russian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee_athletes_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee_athletes_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2952, \"end\": 2957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999976807885, \"rank\": 2.3189862561152066e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other champions Dolgopyat (floor exercise), Liu Yang (still rings) and Zhou Jingyuan (parallel bars) of China, and Max Whitlock (pommel horse) of Great Britain are back as well.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3004, \"end\": 3012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3730657452215107e-26, \"text\": \"Liu Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\"}, {\"begin\": 3031, \"end\": 3035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\", \"score\": 0.8115418515711839, \"rank\": 0.2291044424222887, \"text\": \"Zhou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\"}, {\"begin\": 3064, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9934228937250241, \"rank\": 0.004477937886529896, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3075, \"end\": 3087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 3106, \"end\": 3119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9991050408819454, \"rank\": 0.0008757368396499993, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, Yulo, 24, is up to the challenge.\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I discovered new skills and I know for myself that I can pull them off this time,\\\" said Yulo.\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3270, \"end\": 3274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really aiming to win a medal this time and to have a better performance compared to before.\\\"\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo endured a bumpy journey back to the Olympics as he dealt withissues concerning his career and personal lifein the lead-up to 