aw his split with Kugimiya as a major factor in his supposed drop in performance.\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 4089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3950, \"end\": 3957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"score\": 0.947104850598383, \"rank\": 0.055849268717663804, \"text\": \"Antwerp\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\"}, {\"begin\": 3986, \"end\": 3991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999990682227, \"rank\": 9.319059927802097e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Estranged relationships with some of his family members also surfaced and Yulo recently parted ways with hismanagement group.\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4165, \"end\": 4169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Yulo, though, every experience - be it good or bad - has contributed to his growth.\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4222, \"end\": 4226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will bring everything that I have learned from my past mistakes to this Olympics so that I will be able to produce better results,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4307, \"to\": 4450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo will be joined by Ale